getBuilder

public static <T extends Component> ComponentBuilder<T> getBuilder(T component)
Gets a component builder suitable for building the specific type of component given. The default builder returned is a ComponentBuilder while component types of Field and Container are also catered for.

Type Parameters:
T - The type of the component for which to get a component builder.
Parameters:
component - The component whose builder is to be determined.
Returns:
The builder for the component, or null if the given component is null.
